Acoustic theory

Acoustic theory is a scientific field that relates to the description of <a href="Sound%23Longitudinal_and_transverse_waves">sound waves</a>. It derives from <a href="fluid%20dynamics">fluid dynamics</a>. See <a href="acoustics">acoustics</a> for the <a href="engineering">engineering</a> approach.

